390
00:40:45,100 --> 00:40:46,900
Kvragu!

391
00:40:48,100 --> 00:40:50,200
Gubi se!

392
00:41:04,200 --> 00:41:06,100
Vozi!

393
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:12,300
<i>Engleska se crkva priključila
