00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:31,100
Što to radiš? Ede, pazi!

399
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:37,800
Mislim da smo udarili u nešto.

400
00:41:40,500 --> 00:41:43,800
Ili u nekoga.

