404
00:42:08,200 --> 00:42:10,200
Hvala Bogu.

405
00:42:17,500 --> 00:42:19,300
Vidi ti tu ljepotu.

406
00:42:23,100 --> 00:42:27,600
Nisi mi rekao da Barbara
ima <i>Jaguara</i>. - Philipov je.

