559
00:56:03,100 --> 00:56:07,300
Bog, Liz. Dugo se nismo
vidjele. - Zdravo, Yvonne.

560
00:56:07,500 --> 00:56:12,300
Ovo je moj dečko Declan,
prijatelji Mark i Maggie,

561
00:56:12,500 --> 00:56:15,800
